<p>If you don't need to use this parameter, you can simply pass NULL as this parameter value.</p>

<p>Below is an example of the method's signature:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
 public function formRadio($name, $value = null, $attribs = null,
        $options = null, $listsep = "<br />\n")
    {
         // The method definition is here.
    }
</code></pre>

